  "keyFeatures": [
    "Multi-agent orchestration for Claude Code, GitHub Copilot, Codex, Gemini, and other AI coding agents",
    "Persistent work state via git-backed hooks that survive agent restarts and crashes",
    "Convoy work tracking system bundling multiple beads (issues) for coordinated delivery",
    "Built-in mailbox and inter-agent communication via nudges and mail",
    "Bors-style merge queue (Refinery) with batch-then-bisect verification",
    "Three-tier watchdog system (Witness, Deacon, Boot) for agent health monitoring",
    "Federated work coordination via Wasteland/DoltHub integration",
    "Activity feed TUI (gt feed) and web dashboard for real-time monitoring",
    "Scheduler for capacity-governed polecat dispatch to prevent API rate exhaustion",
    "Formula/molecule system for TOML-defined repeatable multi-step workflows",
    "Seance for querying previous agent sessions and recovering context",
    "OpenTelemetry metrics and structured logging to any OTLP-compatible backend"
  ],
